BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:kLl0pxUWIrgE0eVPCGU9T
SUMMARY:Maddox Batson
DTSTAMP:20260324T020853Z
DTSTART:20260401T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:Maddox Batson\, a teen sensation born in Nashville and raised i
	n Birmingham\, Alabama\, combines modern neo-traditional Country music wit
	h a touch of southern rock and pop. He's a versatile talent\, excelling as
	 a singer/songwriter\, multi-instrument musician\, actor and athlete. Bats
	on's humor and charm shine through his viral social media videos\, amassin
	g over 200M views in under five months and over 3M followers. Born to ente
	rtain\, he brings a unique style that sets him apart. Touted as a "mix bet
	ween Cole Swindell\, Morgan Wallen and Justin Bieber\," he is continuing t
	o hone his craft\, both as a vocalist and as a songwriter for his ever-gro
	wing fan base and hopes to win you over with his genuine smile and infecti
	ous voice. In addition to his two viral track releases "Tears In The River
	" and "I Wanna Know\," Batson has also solidified his spot in the writers 
	room\, most recently landing a cut from global superstars Lana Del Ray and
	 Quavo with "Tough." The rising star will join Gabby Barrett on stage this
